WEBVTT

00:00:00.214 --> 00:00:01.929
Track 10.04

00:00:03.236 --> 00:00:04.093
Narrator: 1

00:00:04.886 --> 00:00:09.314
A: Where are you? Are you at the airport?

00:00:09.712 --> 00:00:13.077
B: No, I’m in a restaurant with Marco!

00:00:14.857 --> 00:00:15.730
Narrator: 2

00:00:17.317 --> 00:00:19.730
A: Is Pasha at work?

00:00:20.111 --> 00:00:22.762
B: No, he’s on holiday.

00:00:24.246 --> 00:00:25.293
Narrator: 3

00:00:26.420 --> 00:00:28.515
A: You could phone Isabella.

00:00:28.674 --> 00:00:29.896
She’s at home.

00:00:30.150 --> 00:00:34.468
B: I don’t have my phone. It’s in the car.

00:00:36.215 --> 00:00:37.279
Narrator: 4

00:00:38.660 --> 00:00:40.549
A: Is Emma at school?

00:00:40.818 --> 00:00:43.326
B: No, she’s in bed.

00:00:44.932 --> 00:00:46.186
Narrator: 5

00:00:47.408 --> 00:00:49.313
A: Are you on the bus?

00:00:50.274 --> 00:00:53.099
B: No, there aren’t any buses.

00:00:53.417 --> 00:00:54.687
I’m in a taxi.

00:00:56.433 --> 00:00:57.703
Narrator: 6

00:00:59.141 --> 00:01:01.252
A: I’m still at the station.

00:01:01.538 --> 00:01:02.839
The train’s late.

00:01:02.934 --> 00:01:07.559
B: Oh dear. Can you text me when you’re on the train?